**Action:** Remove the conditional rendering blocks that show `⌘{item.shortcut}` badges

### 3. Move Drag Handles from Left to Right
**File:** `src/components/Sidebar.tsx`

**Current Implementation (Lines 78-86):**
```tsx
<div
  {...listeners}
  className="cursor-grab active:cursor-grabbing opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity absolute left-0 w-6 h-full flex items-center justify-center"
  title="Drag to reorder"
>
  <span className="text-xs text-text-light-secondary dark:text-text-dark-secondary">⋮⋮</span>
</div>
```

**Proposed:**
- Change `absolute left-0` to `absolute right-0`
- Move after the label span (between label and settings icon)
- Update visual indicator from `⋮⋮` to `⋮⋮` (keep same)

